title: [Saewehna Jungle, Cave]
description: Lapping effortlessly at the moss and algae enshrouded walls of the enclosure, the vividly hued water ripples lazily in ebbs and surges.  The dusky shadows of the cave afford a buffer to the sun, and the hushed music of the falls provides a soothing background.
location: the environs of the Saewehna Lagoon
